<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/header') %>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="hero text-white text-center" style="background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,94,184,0.9), rgba(0,94,184,0.95)), url('/img/stories-hero.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;">
    <div class="container py-5">
      <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold">Wish Stories That Inspire</h1>
      <p class="lead">See how your support brings joy, hope, and strength to children and families</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WISH STORIES GRID -->
  <section class="py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row g-5">

        <!-- Story 1 -->
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class="card-wish h-100 border-0 shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/img/stories/DW.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Emily">
            <div class="card-body p-5">
              <h3 class="text-primary">Emily, age 7</h3>
              <h5>"I wish to go to Disney World"</h5>
              <p class="fs-5">After two years of chemotherapy for leukemia, Emily finally met Cinderella. "It was the best day of my life," she said with the biggest smile.</p>
              <blockquote class="text-muted fst-italic">
                "The wish gave Emily something to look forward to during treatment. It changed everything." — Emily's mom
              </blockquote>
              <a href="/donate" class="btn btn-wish mt-3">Help Grant the Next Wish</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Story 2 -->
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class="card-wish h-100 border-0 shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/img/stories/game.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Jayden">
            <div class="card-body p-5">
              <h3 class="text-primary">Jayden, age 12</h3>
              <h5>"I wish to have a gaming setup"</h5>
              <p class="fs-5">Living with cystic fibrosis, Jayden wanted to play online with friends. His new computer and gaming chair brought him endless joy and connection.</p>
              <blockquote class="text-muted fst-italic">
                "He hasn’t stopped smiling since the wish arrived. Thank you from the bottom of our hearts." — Jayden's dad
              </blockquote>
              <a href="/donate" class="btn btn-wish mt-3">Make Another Wish Come True</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Story 3 -->
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class="card-wish h-100 border-0 shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/img/stories/unicorn.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Ava">
            <div class="card-body p-5">
              <h3 class="text-primary">Ava, age 5</h3>
              <h5>"I wish to meet a real unicorn"</h5>
              <p class="fs-5">Ava’s rare heart condition didn’t stop her dream. We brought a gentle white horse with a glowing horn to her backyard. Magic was real that day.</p>
              <blockquote class="text-muted fst-italic">
                "Ava said it was better than Christmas. Thank you for making her believe again." — Ava's mom
              </blockquote>
              <a href="/donate" class="btn btn-wish mt-3">Help Grant More Magic</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Story 4 -->
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <div class="card-wish h-100 border-0 shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/img/stories/fire.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Mason">
            <div class="card-body p-5">
              <h3 class="text-primary">Mason, age 9</h3>
              <h5>"I wish to be a firefighter for a day"</h5>
              <p class="fs-5">Battling brain cancer, Mason got his own uniform, rode in a fire truck, and put out a "real" fire. He said he felt unstoppable.</p>
              <blockquote class="text-muted fst-italic">
                "This wish reminded Mason he’s a hero — no matter what." — Fire Chief
              </blockquote>
              <a href="/donate" class="btn btn-wish mt-3">Be a Hero Today</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-5">
        <h3>Every child deserves a wish</h3>
        <a href="/donate" class="btn btn-wish btn-lg px-5">Donate Now</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>